Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.39,MH_dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:26.39,napis1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(128,548)}6. duben
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:25.64,MH_dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Opravit to zabere tak 2 až 3 dny, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.90,MH_dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A radši bys to neměl zvorat.
